1
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:15,930
Zhang Haixia...

2
00:00:17,820 --> 00:00:19,330
You're crazy!

3
00:00:27,830 --> 00:00:29,560
Didn't you already know that?

4
00:01:10,800 --> 00:01:11,800
Come back with me.

5
00:01:17,510 --> 00:01:18,440
We can't go back.

6
00:02:38,500 --> 00:02:41,700
Looks like Commander Mo has achieved
his long-held wish.

7
00:02:59,740 --> 00:03:00,910
Is this the true purpose for which you

8
00:03:00,910 --> 00:03:02,710
and Mo Yungao came to Bailejing?

9
00:03:18,550 --> 00:03:19,210
Hailou,

10
00:03:20,510 --> 00:03:22,040
when that day really comes,

11
00:03:23,130 --> 00:03:24,690
you must not go soft on me.

12
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:52,510
Please, Feikun Balu.

13
00:03:52,579 --> 00:03:53,860
Please save us.

14
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,780
Lock all the windows
and go back to your room!

15
00:04:02,780 --> 00:04:04,330
Don't touch these things!

16
00:04:04,500 --> 00:04:07,100
Don't touch these things!
Don't touch them...

17
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:08,360
Don't touch them.

18
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,560
Don't touch them.

19
00:06:23,950 --> 00:06:30,080
[Archives: The Nanyang Mystery]

20
00:06:30,410 --> 00:06:33,130
[Episode 30]

21
00:07:02,130 --> 00:07:02,790
Feng Huang?

22
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:05,900
Feng Huang?

23
00:07:06,990 --> 00:07:07,750
Feng Huang.

24
00:07:10,450 --> 00:07:11,130
Feng Huang.

25
00:07:13,900 --> 00:07:15,360
Thank goodness, it's you.

26
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:17,240
You scared the wits out of me.

27
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,100
I thought...

28
00:07:18,230 --> 00:07:20,430
I thought it was that snake demon again.

29
00:07:20,440 --> 00:07:22,380
Look at you, so sheltered.

30
00:07:22,470 --> 00:07:23,390
So pathetic.

31
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,700
You need to toughen up.

32
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:28,540
What happened to your hands?

33
00:07:28,540 --> 00:07:29,710
What are you staring at?

34
00:07:29,710 --> 00:07:31,170
Hurry up and find a way out.

35
00:07:40,200 --> 00:07:41,260
Let's go. This way.

36
00:07:42,659 --> 00:07:43,270
My leg...

37
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,370
What happened to it?

38
00:07:46,690 --> 00:07:48,190
I... I'll carry you.

39
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:55,500
Let's go this way.

40
00:08:08,100 --> 00:08:09,180
What is this?

41
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:12,940
Something related to
the Zhang family, I guess.

42
00:08:14,490 --> 00:08:16,550
It wasn't until today that I realized

43
00:08:16,740 --> 00:08:18,080
our family

44
00:08:18,350 --> 00:08:20,610
has been battling dangers all this time.

45
00:08:20,690 --> 00:08:22,410
Your family is really strange.

46
00:08:22,410 --> 00:08:23,530
Your siblings

47
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:24,490
are unusual too.

48
00:08:25,330 --> 00:08:26,650
I was adopted.

49
00:08:27,950 --> 00:08:29,060
I was slow as a kid.

50
00:08:29,420 --> 00:08:31,220
I didn't speak until I was seven,

51
00:08:31,460 --> 00:08:33,659
so I was abandoned at the Taoist temple.

52
00:08:34,250 --> 00:08:36,049
I've stood guard all these years

53
00:08:36,890 --> 00:08:38,490
since my master passed away.

54
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:40,030
Guard what?

55
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:42,690
A promise—

56
00:08:44,030 --> 00:08:45,630
to wait for my master's wife.

57
00:08:46,220 --> 00:08:47,120
I've always

58
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:50,580
thought that my master and I
were both fools.

59
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,770
But after seeing my master's wife,

60
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:55,020
I realized I was the bigger fool.

61
00:08:55,620 --> 00:08:56,720
I don't think so.

62
00:08:58,740 --> 00:08:59,720
In this world,

63
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:02,100
most people are
ungrateful and untrustworthy.

64
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:03,830
But your master was different.

65
00:09:03,870 --> 00:09:05,030
He did so much.

66
00:09:05,650 --> 00:09:07,450
I think someone like your master

67
00:09:08,200 --> 00:09:09,200
is hard to come by.

68
00:09:11,670 --> 00:09:13,240
You must've been poisoned

69
00:09:13,360 --> 00:09:15,060
by snake venom
to be saying such kind things.

70
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:16,040
Oh, you...

71
00:09:16,350 --> 00:09:17,960
-I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
-Let's go.

72
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,890
You're so heavy.

73
00:09:41,310 --> 00:09:42,110
Rest in peace,

74
00:09:43,050 --> 00:09:43,620
guys.

75
00:11:03,230 --> 00:11:04,840
Feikun Balu,

76
00:11:05,370 --> 00:11:06,710
you'll save me,

77
00:11:07,590 --> 00:11:08,330
right?

78
00:12:36,790 --> 00:12:37,590
Commander...

79
00:12:40,350 --> 00:12:41,330
Commander.

80
00:12:42,810 --> 00:12:43,960
Commander...

81
00:12:45,170 --> 00:12:45,980
Snake Master?

82
00:12:45,980 --> 00:12:48,730
I've been serving you for so long.

83
00:12:49,290 --> 00:12:50,600
Save me.

84
00:12:50,620 --> 00:12:53,470
Aren't you snake handlers supposed to be
immune to poison?

85
00:12:53,470 --> 00:12:54,690
Save me...

86
00:12:58,770 --> 00:13:01,750
It seems this is goodbye forever.

87
00:13:02,550 --> 00:13:03,530
Farewell.

88
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,380
Tough luck for you.

89
00:13:06,230 --> 00:13:07,090
Commander...

90
00:13:14,760 --> 00:13:17,190
This day has finally come.

91
00:13:18,770 --> 00:13:21,660
Zhang Qiling will be here soon.

92
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,120
Get ready.

93
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:24,680
Yes, sir!

94
00:13:27,350 --> 00:13:29,410
Since we have no more Twilight Grass,

95
00:13:29,620 --> 00:13:31,750
bring out our guns and cannons,

96
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:35,390
and line up to welcome the immortal.

97
00:13:40,150 --> 00:13:41,720
Zhang Qiling,

98
00:13:42,600 --> 00:13:44,870
look at the Twilight Grass everywhere

99
00:13:44,870 --> 00:13:47,200
and corpses scattered across the ground.

100
00:13:47,470 --> 00:13:49,250
Twenty years.

101
00:13:50,240 --> 00:13:52,890
Surely, you'll show yourself this time.

102
00:13:56,030 --> 00:13:58,390
[Young Mo Yungao]

103
00:14:23,330 --> 00:14:23,960
Look,

104
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:25,570
that guy is eating slop,

105
00:14:25,680 --> 00:14:27,280
fighting with dogs for food.

106
00:14:27,410 --> 00:14:29,310
Yeah, like a fool.

107
00:14:29,740 --> 00:14:30,600
-Let's go.
-Go.

108
00:14:39,700 --> 00:14:40,720
What does this say?

109
00:14:40,720 --> 00:14:42,050
Join the ranks!

110
00:14:42,110 --> 00:14:43,520
Food and pay provided!

111
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,390
Join the ranks!

112
00:14:45,390 --> 00:14:46,720
Food and pay provided!

113
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,530
About face!

114
00:14:49,890 --> 00:14:50,600
Attention!

115
00:14:52,970 --> 00:14:53,930
Mo Yungao!

116
00:14:55,170 --> 00:14:55,770
Present!

117
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:56,490
Step out!

118
00:14:56,720 --> 00:14:57,270
Yes, sir!

119
00:14:58,450 --> 00:14:59,190
Aim.

120
00:15:02,290 --> 00:15:02,950
Kneel down.

121
00:15:05,220 --> 00:15:06,080
Kneel down!

122
00:15:08,590 --> 00:15:09,120
Yes, sir.

123
00:15:16,970 --> 00:15:18,030
Move forward a bit.

124
00:15:38,880 --> 00:15:40,610
Don't drag your feet. Hurry up!

125
00:15:41,550 --> 00:15:43,210
One, two!

126
00:15:47,530 --> 00:15:48,250
Mo Yungao!

127
00:15:48,660 --> 00:15:49,190
Present!

128
00:15:49,700 --> 00:15:50,630
Halt!

129
00:15:57,340 --> 00:15:58,980
Sir, what are your orders?

130
00:16:03,330 --> 00:16:03,790
Well...

131
00:16:06,720 --> 00:16:07,250
Hurry up.

132
00:16:12,340 --> 00:16:12,870
Yes, sir.

133
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:41,590
Platoon Leader Mo, your hat.

134
00:16:53,590 --> 00:16:54,560
Platoon Leader Mo.

135
00:16:54,560 --> 00:16:55,170
Present!

136
00:16:55,930 --> 00:16:56,660
Do your best.

137
00:16:57,530 --> 00:16:58,060
Yes, sir!

138
00:16:59,880 --> 00:17:00,940
[Southwestern Bandit Suppression
Campaign Plan]

139
00:17:02,270 --> 00:17:03,330
Platoon Leader Mo.

140
00:17:04,310 --> 00:17:04,839
Present.

141
00:17:05,260 --> 00:17:06,900
You're not getting any younger.

142
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:08,760
Opportunities don't come often.

143
00:17:10,760 --> 00:17:12,160
I have high hopes for you.

144
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:15,099
Thank you, sir.

145
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:25,560
[Zhang Qiling, Chief of the Zhang Family]

146
00:18:25,710 --> 00:18:26,270
Report.

147
00:18:26,940 --> 00:18:28,420
[Investigation Report on
the Hidden Gifted in Nanqiang]

148
00:18:27,530 --> 00:18:30,570
The higher-ups have been
conducting research like this all along.

149
00:18:30,570 --> 00:18:32,070
Someone this extraordinary

150
00:18:32,070 --> 00:18:35,800
could be of tremendous value
to our future military preparedness.

151
00:18:36,030 --> 00:18:36,790
Mo Yungao.

152
00:18:36,790 --> 00:18:37,320
Present.

153
00:18:38,590 --> 00:18:39,850
Can you still find him?

154
00:18:42,580 --> 00:18:43,610
Yes, sir!

155
00:19:06,290 --> 00:19:07,550
Battalion Commander Mo,

156
00:19:07,550 --> 00:19:09,280
we've discovered a rare plant.

157
00:19:09,450 --> 00:19:10,610
It's highly toxic

158
00:19:10,630 --> 00:19:11,910
but hard to cultivate.

159
00:19:12,630 --> 00:19:14,390
We searched all of Nanqiang

160
00:19:14,610 --> 00:19:16,540
but still couldn't find its seeds.

161
00:19:22,710 --> 00:19:24,240
Use every means necessary.

162
00:19:24,280 --> 00:19:25,590
You must find them.

163
00:20:18,890 --> 00:20:19,520
Search!

164
00:20:37,670 --> 00:20:38,320
Sir,

165
00:20:39,360 --> 00:20:40,730
I have figured out a way

166
00:20:40,780 --> 00:20:42,410
to force out the Gifted.

167
00:20:43,120 --> 00:20:43,910
Do you think

168
00:20:44,670 --> 00:20:47,800
you could grant me authority
to mobilize more soldiers?

169
00:20:48,010 --> 00:20:49,140
When the time comes,

170
00:20:49,370 --> 00:20:50,770
I guarantee I'll help you

171
00:20:50,810 --> 00:20:52,290
achieve great success.

172
00:20:58,100 --> 00:20:59,340
Hello, Battalion Commander!

173
00:20:59,340 --> 00:21:01,000
Hello, Battalion Commander!

174
00:21:11,690 --> 00:21:14,620
Next, let's welcome
Division Commander Mo to speak.

175
00:21:40,020 --> 00:21:41,020
Please be seated.

176
00:21:45,160 --> 00:21:46,620
Thank you all.

177
00:21:47,910 --> 00:21:49,880
From today onward, we must

178
00:21:50,850 --> 00:21:53,110
work together with complete sincerity.

179
00:21:55,250 --> 00:21:57,250
I'll still need to rely on all of you.

180
00:21:59,470 --> 00:22:01,900
Today, I only have three points to make.

181
00:22:03,070 --> 00:22:03,790
First,

182
00:22:04,050 --> 00:22:07,110
all operations are to follow my command.

183
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:09,090
Then,

184
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:11,680
for the second point,

185
00:22:12,920 --> 00:22:14,650
don't say more than you need to.

186
00:22:15,850 --> 00:22:16,720
Third,

187
00:22:17,210 --> 00:22:18,650
you must be absolutely clear

188
00:22:18,650 --> 00:22:20,880
whose orders you're supposed to follow.

189
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:21,920
Mine!

190
00:22:25,180 --> 00:22:25,960
Commander,

191
00:22:26,460 --> 00:22:29,520
what exactly is this method
for drawing out the Gifted?

192
00:22:30,180 --> 00:22:31,630
For so many years...

193
00:22:33,760 --> 00:22:34,810
how has this person

194
00:22:34,810 --> 00:22:37,640
managed to leave no trace whatsoever?

195
00:22:39,070 --> 00:22:42,270
The Gifted is drawn to
strange and mysterious phenomena.

196
00:22:43,330 --> 00:22:45,680
Then I'll create them.

197
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,310
If I can't find him,

198
00:22:48,590 --> 00:22:50,450
why not make him come to me?

199
00:22:50,920 --> 00:22:51,750
That...

200
00:22:52,540 --> 00:22:54,360
That Evil God statue.

201
00:22:55,050 --> 00:22:56,400
I've already found

202
00:22:56,500 --> 00:22:58,270
the person who can control it.

203
00:22:58,810 --> 00:23:01,510
As long as we spread the statues out...

204
00:23:03,070 --> 00:23:04,880
we can use them as bait.

205
00:23:05,640 --> 00:23:06,770
How does that sound?

206
00:23:19,010 --> 00:23:20,540
Look at these Evil God statues.

207
00:23:20,540 --> 00:23:22,240
They are the same type as
the one from earlier,

208
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,220
but they look like

209
00:23:23,220 --> 00:23:25,220
they were made in different places.

210
00:23:27,530 --> 00:23:29,090
You're asking me why?

211
00:23:29,090 --> 00:23:29,850
Run!

212
00:23:40,180 --> 00:23:41,110
Keep searching!

213
00:23:44,380 --> 00:23:46,040
If the Evil God Project fails,

214
00:23:46,520 --> 00:23:47,580
then I'm finished.

215
00:23:53,690 --> 00:23:55,490
I still have the Twilight Grass.

216
00:23:56,070 --> 00:23:57,730
We can pull off a Twilight Grass project.

217
00:23:57,730 --> 00:23:58,880
Tell Chen Xifeng

218
00:23:58,910 --> 00:24:00,380
to find the seeds quickly.

219
00:24:00,410 --> 00:24:01,440
Otherwise,

220
00:24:02,350 --> 00:24:04,040
you will be the seeds.

221
00:24:09,100 --> 00:24:11,390
[Many years later]

222
00:24:20,660 --> 00:24:21,970
Fortunately, I have not failed you.

223
00:24:21,970 --> 00:24:24,050
I've obtained the Twilight Grass seeds

224
00:24:24,050 --> 00:24:25,950
and fulfilled your instructions.

225
00:24:25,950 --> 00:24:27,380
Please be careful

226
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:31,060
of the Southern Archives under
the Maritime Supervisory Office.

227
00:24:31,310 --> 00:24:31,980
Commander,

228
00:24:33,270 --> 00:24:34,300
I've already

229
00:24:34,320 --> 00:24:35,720
been to various places

230
00:24:35,780 --> 00:24:36,840
and investigated,

231
00:24:37,380 --> 00:24:39,620
but found no trace of
the so-called Southern Archives.

232
00:24:39,620 --> 00:24:41,530
However, we've captured several people

233
00:24:41,530 --> 00:24:43,330
suspected to be members of the Archives.

234
00:24:43,330 --> 00:24:45,190
Some of them revealed a few clues.

235
00:24:47,140 --> 00:24:47,940
The Southern Archives

236
00:24:47,940 --> 00:24:49,720
is an organization that specializes
in investigating mysterious incidents.

237
00:24:49,720 --> 00:24:51,920
Its top leader is Director Zhang Haiqi.

238
00:24:52,190 --> 00:24:55,390
And the person you're looking for
is called Zhang Qiling.

239
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:59,210
You're saying his name is Zhang Qiling?

240
00:25:03,110 --> 00:25:04,130
Where is he now?

241
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:05,100
I don't know.

242
00:25:05,120 --> 00:25:06,660
The last I heard,

243
00:25:07,180 --> 00:25:09,310
Zhang Qiling had appeared in Nanqiang

244
00:25:09,390 --> 00:25:11,030
and stayed there for quite some time.

245
00:25:11,030 --> 00:25:13,120
Seemed like
something was about to emerge there.

246
00:25:13,120 --> 00:25:14,670
If you want to know more,

247
00:25:14,700 --> 00:25:15,980
you can go to the Archives

248
00:25:15,980 --> 00:25:17,910
and look up files
with lower serial numbers.

249
00:25:17,910 --> 00:25:19,910
They contain records
of the Zhang family's core members

250
00:25:19,910 --> 00:25:20,970
and their secrets.

251
00:25:21,140 --> 00:25:22,070
But first,

252
00:25:22,070 --> 00:25:24,250
you need to find out
where the Archives is.

253
00:25:24,250 --> 00:25:25,070
So,

254
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:27,110
you still need to find Zhang Haiqi.

255
00:25:31,080 --> 00:25:34,680
The Pitcher Plant Project can be
set in motion ahead of schedule.

256
00:25:35,790 --> 00:25:36,320
Yes, sir.

257
00:25:51,010 --> 00:25:51,670
Commander.

258
00:25:55,310 --> 00:25:57,250
Had a good time with your friend?

259
00:26:10,670 --> 00:26:13,200
Those weapons are all
meant for Zhang Qiling?

260
00:26:14,260 --> 00:26:16,860
I don't think those will be enough.
You'll die.

261
00:26:16,940 --> 00:26:17,670
And besides,

262
00:26:19,340 --> 00:26:21,800
how can you be sure
he'll definitely appear?

263
00:26:24,200 --> 00:26:26,250
Well, he is Feikun Balu.

264
00:26:26,310 --> 00:26:28,310
Now that I've destroyed Bailejing,

265
00:26:28,530 --> 00:26:29,770
he's bound to show up.

266
00:26:36,000 --> 00:26:39,130
We've nearly finished researching
the Twilight Grass.

267
00:26:39,140 --> 00:26:41,270
It's time to shift to studying people.

268
00:26:42,830 --> 00:26:44,720
I once fought seven others

269
00:26:45,100 --> 00:26:46,320
to the death.

270
00:26:47,090 --> 00:26:48,440
We tore into each other,

271
00:26:48,750 --> 00:26:49,900
biting like dogs,

272
00:26:51,880 --> 00:26:54,000
all for half a steamed bun like this.

273
00:26:55,260 --> 00:26:56,660
This is what people are.

274
00:26:59,720 --> 00:27:01,090
Boring.

275
00:27:03,750 --> 00:27:04,980
So now,

276
00:27:05,910 --> 00:27:07,960
I'd rather study immortals.

277
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:09,410
The moment Zhang Qiling appears,

278
00:27:09,410 --> 00:27:10,630
capture him alive.

279
00:27:12,290 --> 00:27:14,950
Those weapons can
wipe out an entire battalion.

280
00:27:15,500 --> 00:27:17,000
No matter how powerful Zhang Qiling is,

281
00:27:17,000 --> 00:27:18,910
he can't withstand modern firearms, right?

282
00:27:18,910 --> 00:27:20,600
Unless he resorts to tricks.

283
00:27:20,630 --> 00:27:22,160
How do we capture him alive?

284
00:27:22,290 --> 00:27:24,310
You'll have to ask
Adjutant Zhang about that.

285
00:27:24,310 --> 00:27:25,330
He has an idea.

286
00:27:25,810 --> 00:27:27,470
I rarely ask favors of anyone.

287
00:27:27,550 --> 00:27:29,270
I finally asked him for one.

288
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:31,730
He'll certainly come through for me.
Right?

289
00:27:34,620 --> 00:27:35,380
Commander,

290
00:27:36,230 --> 00:27:37,190
you helped me,

291
00:27:37,930 --> 00:27:39,460
so naturally I'll help you.

292
00:27:39,900 --> 00:27:41,760
But first, you need to understand

293
00:27:42,230 --> 00:27:43,690
what kind of place this is.

294
00:27:47,640 --> 00:27:49,100
Don't you find it strange?

295
00:27:49,670 --> 00:27:52,000
Why is Zhang Qiling
so drawn to this place?

296
00:27:53,700 --> 00:27:56,060
Why have
the Twilight Grass experiments here

297
00:27:56,060 --> 00:27:57,720
been such a complete success?

298
00:27:59,340 --> 00:28:00,470
Twenty years apart,

299
00:28:00,890 --> 00:28:03,020
and now returning to the same place...

300
00:28:05,140 --> 00:28:07,140
do you really think that's fate?

301
00:28:17,520 --> 00:28:20,110
Then you tell me. Why?

302
00:28:21,180 --> 00:28:22,630
Explain to me...

303
00:28:25,000 --> 00:28:26,460
what kind of place this is.

304
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:38,810
Commander Mo's orders—

305
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:40,560
capture Zhang Qiling alive!

306
00:29:00,770 --> 00:29:01,850
You really came.

307
00:29:13,950 --> 00:29:15,010
Someone is coming.

308
00:30:06,780 --> 00:30:07,910
Why just one person?

309
00:30:22,850 --> 00:30:24,330
Feikun Balu has appeared!

310
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:26,030
Feikun Balu!

311
00:30:27,030 --> 00:30:27,960
Feikun Balu.

312
00:30:31,420 --> 00:30:32,430
Feikun Balu.

313
00:30:33,570 --> 00:30:35,090
You are no match for those people.

314
00:30:35,090 --> 00:30:36,590
Are we just going to let them

315
00:30:36,590 --> 00:30:38,140
murder our families?

316
00:30:38,370 --> 00:30:39,580
Go back immediately

317
00:30:39,670 --> 00:30:41,550
and protect those who are still alive.

318
00:30:41,550 --> 00:30:43,590
Don't let yourself
come into contact with the grass fluff.

319
00:30:43,590 --> 00:30:44,990
Leave those people to me.

320
00:30:45,660 --> 00:30:47,250
I'll end all of this.

321
00:31:49,770 --> 00:31:50,940
Zhang Qiling.

322
00:32:05,100 --> 00:32:06,510
He's really here.

323
00:32:19,770 --> 00:32:20,780
I want him alive.

324
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:23,030
None of you are allowed to harm him.

325
00:32:23,030 --> 00:32:24,450
I... I want him alive.

326
00:33:25,590 --> 00:33:26,560
Come out,

327
00:33:27,180 --> 00:33:28,250
Mo Yungao.

328
00:33:40,420 --> 00:33:41,340
Commander Mo.

329
00:33:43,300 --> 00:33:45,910
It seems your fate is sealed today.

330
00:34:03,420 --> 00:34:04,220
Cover the Commander!

331
00:34:04,220 --> 00:34:05,420
Cover the Commander!

332
00:34:43,050 --> 00:34:44,010
Commander Mo,

333
00:34:44,460 --> 00:34:46,880
it seems your fate is sealed today.

334
00:34:49,000 --> 00:34:50,560
But I can help you.

335
00:34:51,070 --> 00:34:51,920
You retreat.

336
00:34:52,860 --> 00:34:54,060
I'll take your place.

337
00:35:18,760 --> 00:35:20,020
He's not Zhang Qiling.

338
00:35:24,820 --> 00:35:26,710
Even though he's not Zhang Qiling,

339
00:35:26,710 --> 00:35:28,510
he still gets to be the immortal?

340
00:35:32,610 --> 00:35:33,360
Why?

341
00:35:38,200 --> 00:35:39,600
What gives you the right?

342
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:47,780
Zhang Haixia.

343
00:35:49,650 --> 00:35:51,850
Mo Yungao has harmed countless people.

344
00:35:52,480 --> 00:35:53,690
Why did you help him?

345
00:35:56,090 --> 00:35:58,000
Do you know why you failed?

346
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,650
Because I know you too well.

347
00:36:03,280 --> 00:36:04,280
You're still you.

348
00:36:06,150 --> 00:36:08,080
But I'm not who I used to be anymore.

349
00:36:09,670 --> 00:36:11,380
If you want to kill me,

350
00:36:13,180 --> 00:36:14,910
then you'll have to change.

351
00:37:03,010 --> 00:37:04,240
Would an immortal

352
00:37:04,800 --> 00:37:06,260
like bullets?
